channel.title: JDK problem
channel.description:
Hey guys,
I'm totaly new to programming & I've just made my own server.. I've used the allstar-scape v1 source & its going okay (Before you flame the source It was the only one I saw when I was looking, so picked it 1st) I know its not the best but it'll do for now, anyway.. I edited shit loads of things in Gui & client.java ect... to cut to the chase I have downloaded [b]JDK 6.0 Java developing Program[/b] and it used to work fine (few months ago) and now since I started coding again it messes up.
When I try to compile it says [IMG]http://i973.photobucket.com/albums/ae213/mr0wn/error.jpg[/img] now can anyone explain my problem (I've already downloaded the latest normal Java.)
~ Josh
